ack\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mus1665702918972.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mus1665702918972.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mus1665702918972.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mus1665702918972\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Supplies Uniface with the result of an aggregate computation in the Select mode 4 connector request.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mus1665702918972__topic_d131648e1_d131649e1_d131650e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131651e1_d131652e1_d131653e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">void usumfld</code>(<var class=\"keyword varname\">uc, result, length, pack</var>)</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131654e1_d131655e1_d131656e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">struct uctrl</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">*uc</var>;</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131657e1_d131658e1_d131659e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">unsigned char</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">*result</var>;</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131660e1_d131661e1_d131662e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">short</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">length</var>;</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131663e1_d131664e1_d131665e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">short</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">pack</var>;</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mus1665702918972__section_s5m_wst_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872557e98\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"mus1665702918972__parml_htw_yst_gwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">uc</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Address of the current control block.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">result</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Pointer to the result value.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">length</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Length of the result value pointed to by <var class=\"keyword varname\">result</var>.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">pack</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Connector-level packing code of the result value.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mus1665702918972__section_vxy_ctt_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872557e150\">Return values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Not applicable.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mus1665702918972__section_jjt_qwz_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d872557e159\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Supplies Uniface with the result of an aggregate computation in the Select mode 4\n            connector request. <code class=\"ph codeph\">usumfld</code> must be called once for every entry in the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">uordlst</code> structure. Calls to <code class=\"ph codeph\">usumfld</code> must be in the\n            same order as the entries appear in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uordlst</code> structure.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131681e1_d131682e1_d131683e1\">The following example assumes the results of the\n            calculation of aggregates is already known and can be accessed through an SQL descriptor\n            area (SQLDA). This example is based on the DEC Rdb API, the implementation of the data\n            structures used can differ for other APIs.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131684e1_d131685e1_d131686e1\">The following function is called in the\n            example:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131687e1_d131688e1_d131689e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MapDBMSToPackingCode</code>—Fetch the\n            next record from the specified (open) cursor and update the values in SQLDA.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mus1665702918972__p_d131690e1_d131691e1_d131692e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">DrvAdminType</code> data type is\n            created for this example, it holds the PRA in its PRA field. Such a structure would\n            usually be stored in the connector workspace (<code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrv</code>).</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mus1665702918972_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mus1665702918972__codeblock_abm_ktt_gwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">ReturnAggregatesToUniface (struct uctrl *ControlBlock,\nSQLDA *DescriptorArea )\n{\nSQLVAR *SQLVar;\nint i;\nlong LengthToReturn;\nshort TypeToReturn;\nfor ( SQLVar = DescriptorArea-&gt;sqlvar, i = 0;\ni &lt; DescriptorArea-&gt;sqld;/* sqld gives the number */\nSQLVar++, i++ ) /* of sqlvar elements present.*/\n{\nif ( SQLVar-&gt;sqlind == -1 ) /* Indicates a NULL value. */\n{\nLengthToReturn = 0; /* This way a NULL value is */\nTypeToReturn = pC; /* reported to UNIFACE. */\n}\nelse\n{\nLengthToReturn = SQLVar-&gt;sqllen;\nTypeToReturn = MapDBMSTypeToPackingCode ( SQLVar-&gt;sqltype,\nLengthToReturn );\n}\nusumfld (ControlBlock,\n(unsigned char *)SQLVar-&gt;sqldata,\nLengthToReturn,\nTypeToReturn );\n}\n}\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pcd1665702916314.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uordlst</a><p>Describes the requested ordering of selected records.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530089\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530089\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "usumfld Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Supplies Uniface with the result of an aggregate computation in the Select mode 4 connector request. void usumfld ( uc, result, length, pack ) struct uctrl *uc ; unsigned char *result ; short length ; short pack ; Parameters uc Address of the current control block. result Pointer to the result value. length Length of the result value pointed to by result . pack Connector-level packing code of the result value. Return values Not applicable. Description Supplies Uniface with the result of an aggregate computation in the Select mode 4 connector request. usumfld must be called once for every entry in the uordlst structure. Calls to usumfld must be in the same order as the entries appear in the uordlst structure. The following example assumes the results of the calculation of aggregates is already known and can be accessed through an SQL descriptor area (SQLDA). This example is based on the DEC Rdb API, the implementation of the data structures used can differ for other APIs. The following function is called in the example: MapDBMSToPackingCode —Fetch the next record from the specified (open) cursor and update the values in SQLDA. The DrvAdminType data type is created for this example, it holds the PRA in its PRA field. Such a structure would usually be stored in the connector workspace ( uctrl->udrv ). Explain this code ReturnAggregatesToUniface (struct uctrl *ControlBlock, SQLDA *DescriptorArea ) { SQLVAR *SQLVar; int i; long LengthToReturn; short TypeToReturn; for ( SQLVar = DescriptorArea->sqlvar, i = 0; i < DescriptorArea->sqld;/* sqld gives the number */ SQLVar++, i++ ) /* of sqlvar elements present.*/ { if ( SQLVar->sqlind == -1 ) /* Indicates a NULL value. */ { LengthToReturn = 0; /* This way a NULL value is */ TypeToReturn = pC; /* reported to UNIFACE. */ } else { LengthToReturn = SQLVar->sqllen; TypeToReturn = MapDBMSTypeToPackingCode ( SQLVar->sqltype, LengthToReturn ); } usumfld (ControlBlock, (unsigned char *)SQLVar->sqldata, LengthToReturn, TypeToReturn ); } } Copy Related Links uordlst Describes the requested ordering of selected records. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}